44
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,600
You just haven't admitted it yet.

45
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,880
So we are kind of...

46
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,630
A future couple?

47
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:39,860
Yes.

48
00:05:40,730 --> 00:05:42,200
You guys just need a moment

49
