Hongze Funeral Directors.

97
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,409
We have a lot of opportunities

98
00:08:36,429 --> 00:08:37,590
to work with him in the future.

99
00:08:38,770 --> 00:08:39,890
An important partner?

100
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:17,950
As the successor, you need to take care of your appearance.

101
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,820
It's a sign of respect for the clients,

102
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,080
and also for yourself.

103
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,150
I don't like wearing suits.

104
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,270
My first suit

105
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,820
was a disaster.

106
00:09:31,730 --> 00:09:34,000
When I was a little boy, my brother forced me to wear a suit

107
00:09:34,020 --> 00:09:35,320
to attend a relatives' wedding.

108
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:38,320
At that time, my suit felt tight,

109
00:09:39,010 --> 00:09:39,940
and I accidentally spilled a drink

110
00:09:39,940 --> 00:09:40,960
on the bride.

111
00:09:44,510 --> 00:09:47,310
My first suit was given to me by my dad as a gift.

112
00:09:50,270 --> 00:09:53,480
He said a suit represents a man's maturity

113
00:09:54,310 --> 00:09:55,600
and also his responsibility.

114
00:09:56,950 --> 00:09:58,590
He hopes I can take good care of myself,

115
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,100
and more importantly, understand the importance of giving to others.

116
00:10:02,530 --> 00:10:03,440
I've always

117
00:10:05,090 --> 00:10:06,130
remembered that.

118
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:19,790
This seems to be the first time.

119
00:10:20,410 --> 00:10:21,050
The first time?

120
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:25,220
